      <bioghist id="aspace_0c2140a5576c375dc90152d57aa7ee3a">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Bryant F. Tolles graduated with a Bachelor of Arts from Yale College in 1923. He was a member of the Beta Theta Pi fraternity and served in the Students Army Training Corps, Yale University.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_e2bbd42e1b2b928e42b753866491177b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of printed material and a paddle relating to the Phi Chi chapter of Beta Theta Pi fraternity, a photograph, one letter, an enlistment record, and a trophy.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
